## Pivot table and create new total columns


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
df |> 
  pivot_longer(
    cols = !c(region, status, area),
    names_to = "year",
    values_to = "counts"
  ) |> 
  pivot_wider(
    names_from = c(status, area),
    values_from = counts
  ) |> 
  rowwise() |> 
  mutate(
    marriage_total = sum(marriage_city, marriage_village),
    divorce_total = sum(divorce_city, divorce_village)
  ) -> gt_df

gt_df |> 
  kable() |> 
  head()
```

